{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0a98d25f14","title":"毛泽东对大树特树绝对权威的提法等的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"984d799dc5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"0a98d25f14"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f6c0e6fb36","type":"title","text":"对大树特树绝对权威的提法等的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"19d6bed8bb","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"ecddf52979","type":"appellation","text":"林、周、中央及文革各同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"5196847a9c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）绝对权威的提法不妥。从来没有单独的绝对权威，凡权威都是相对的，凡绝对的东西都只存在相对的东西之中，犹如绝对真理是无数相对真理的总和，绝对真理只存在于各个相对真理之中一样。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"e8b265ec17","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）大树特树的说法也不妥。权威或威信只能从斗争实践中自然地建立，不能由人工去建立，这样建立的威信必然会垮下来。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"757c99f496","type":"paragraph","text":"（三） 党中央很早就禁止祝寿，应通知全国重申此种禁令。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"6b6bd352f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（四） 湖南的集会应另择日期。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"8b24bcc712","type":"paragraph","text":"（五） 我们不要题字。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"5bc635e45e","type":"paragraph","text":"（六） 会议名称，可同意湖南建议，用第一方案。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"},{"id":"50cab8b29d","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点请在一次会议上讨论通过为盼。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14"}],"page":{"id":"7631385521","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0a98d25f14","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}